-- PRef(psia)  Bw(rb/stb)  Cw(psi-1)   Visc(cP)  Viscosibility
    4017.55     1.038       3.22E-6      0.318      0.0 /

ROCK
-- PRef(psia)  Cr(psi-1)
    14.7        3E-6 /

