DENSITY
-- Oil(lb/ft3)  Water(lb/ft3)  Gas(lb/ft3)
   53.66        64.49          0.0533 /

PVDG
--  P(psia)   Bg(rb/Mscf)   Visc(cP)
     14.700   166.666        0.00800
    264.700    12.093        0.00960
